                        <interp inst="t18380709-name-118" type="surname" value="SEATON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380709-name-118" type="given" value="ANN ESTHER"></interp>ANN ESTHER SEATON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of John Seaton, and live at Queen-row, Hoxton Old Town. My door is a few doors from the pro<lb></lb>secutor's—I saw the prisoner there—he made many attempts to get the veil down with a cane, and he got it, and put it inside his waistcoat—I watched him for a quarter of an hour.</p>
